title: Taylor Swift Searches Blocked by X Amid Circulation of Deepfakes
description: X, formerly Twitter, blocked searches of Taylor Swift's name to crack down on deepfakes.

title: Three American Troops Killed In Drone Attack by Iran-Backed Militia in Jordan, Says Biden
description: Three American troops were killed and “many” were wounded Sunday in a drone strike in northeast Jordan near the Syrian border.

title: Protesters Just Targeted the Mona Lisa by Throwing Soup at the Masterpiece. Here’s Why
description: Two environmental activists threw soup on Leonardo da Vinci’s 'Mona Lisa' painting in the Louvre Museum in Paris.

title: U.N. Chief Calls for Resumed Funding of Palestinian Aid Agency Amid Allegations of Militant Ties
description: The U.N. secretary-general called on countries to resume funding the aid agency amid allegations some staff were involved in Hamas' attack.

title: Biden Says He Would Shut Down Border ‘Right Now’ if Congress Sends Him a Deal
description: Biden offered fresh assurances that he would be willing to close the U.S.-Mexico border if lawmakers would only send him a bill to sign.
